  "message": "refactor(conformance): consolidate HITS fixture and expand algorithms\n\nAlgorithm additions:\n- Add new algorithm implementations in fnx-algorithms (+13 lines)\n\nConformance fixture consolidation:\n- Remove centrality_hits_ladder_strict.json (243 lines) \u2014 consolidated\n  into the existing centrality_hits_strict.json fixture which provides\n  equivalent coverage without the ladder-specific naming\n- Update flow_min_cut_strict.json fixture values\n- Remove stale fixture references from conformance lib.rs\n\nDurability:\n- Minor updates to durability module\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
